<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/20527111">思维跳跃性强是否是想象力丰富的表现？是否是逻辑性思维欠缺的表现？什么又是逻辑？数学好代表逻辑就强吗？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="391323" data-action="/question/detail">

